017package org.apache.bcel.classfile;
018
019import java.io.DataInput;
020import java.io.DataOutputStream;
021import java.io.IOException;
022
023import org.apache.bcel.Const;
024
025/**
026 * An annotation that is represented in the class file and is provided to the JVM.
027 *
028 * @since 6.0
029 */
030public class RuntimeVisibleAnnotations extends Annotations {
031
032    /**
033     * Constructs a new instance.
034     *
035     * @param nameIndex Index pointing to the name <em>Code</em>
036     * @param length Content length in bytes
037     * @param input Input stream
038     * @param constantPool Array of constants
039     * @throws IOException Thrown when an I/O exception of some sort has occurred.
040     */
041    public RuntimeVisibleAnnotations(final int nameIndex, final int length, final DataInput input, final ConstantPool constantPool) throws IOException {
042        super(Const.ATTR_RUNTIME_VISIBLE_ANNOTATIONS, nameIndex, length, input, constantPool, true);
043    }
044
045    /**
046     * Creates a deep copy of this attribute.
047     *
048     * @return deep copy of this attribute.
049     */
050    @Override
051    public Attribute copy(final ConstantPool constantPool) {
052        return (Attribute) clone();
053    }
054
055    @Override
056    public final void dump(final DataOutputStream dos) throws IOException {
057        super.dump(dos);
058        writeAnnotations(dos);
059    }
060}
